99
00:04:31,420 --> 00:04:33,050
So it could be the
Jack of hearts,

100
00:04:33,050 --> 00:04:35,414
or it could be the
Jack of diamonds,

101
00:04:35,414 --> 00:04:36,830
or it could be the
Jack of spades,

102
00:04:36,830 --> 00:04:38,450
or it could be the
Queen of hearts,

103
00:04:38,450 --> 00:04:39,872
or it could be
