104
00:04:39,872 --> 00:04:41,330
So what is the
probability of this?

105
00:04:41,330 --> 00:04:43,579
And this is a little bit
more of an interesting thing,

106
00:04:43,579 --> 00:04:46,440
because we know, first
of all, that there

107
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:49,912
